Package com.cloudera.cdk.data.spi

Provides a service provider interface for implementors of CDK Data APIs.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
Loadable This interface is used to load classes via a ServiceLoader.
OptionBuilder<T> This interface defines methods that allow instances of some type, T, to be created from a set of options.
 

Class Summary
AbstractDataset<E> A common Dataset base class to simplify implementations.
AbstractDatasetReader<E> A common DatasetReader base class to simplify implementations.
AbstractDatasetRepository A common DatasetRepository base class to simplify implementation.
AbstractMetadataProvider A common DatasetRepository base class to simplify implementation.
AbstractRangeView<E> A common View base class to simplify implementations of Views created from ranges.
CompleteKey A CompleteKey is a Marker that is complete for a PartitionStrategy.
Conversions Static helper methods for converting between types.
Marker A Marker is a bookmark in the partition space, which is the space of each possible partition in a PartitionStrategy.
Marker.Builder A fluent builder for creating Marker instances.
MarkerComparator Comparison methods for Marker objects with respect to a PartitionStrategy.
MarkerRange Represents a range of concrete partitions.
MarkerRange.Boundary Represents the boundary of a range, either inclusive or exclusive.
URIPattern Defines a URI pattern that can be used to parse and match other URIs.
 

Enum Summary
ReaderWriterState An enum representing the state of a DatasetReader or DatasetWriter.
